	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Author of a law requiring consecrations of buildings, areas, and altars to be specifically ordered by the people (Cic. Dom. 127-128). Probably after 174 (cf. Liv. 40.52.1) and before 154 (Cic. Dom. 130 and 136). See Niccolini, FTP 403f." .
